	abstract = {Detection and visualization of the cannabinoid receptor type 2 by a cell-permeable high affinity fluorescent probe platform enables tracing receptor trafficking in live cells and in zebrafish.
          , 
            
              Despite its essential role in the (patho)physiology of several diseases, CB
              2
